<section id="mission">
  <h2>Mission</h2>
  <p>
    We help teams build digital products that are accessible by default, inclusive in design, and aligned with Government of Canada standards.
  </p>

  <h3>How we collaborate</h3>
  <p>
    We partner early with service and delivery teams to reduce barriers before they reach production.
  </p>

  <h3>How we improve outcomes</h3>
  <p>
    We combine practical guidance, reusable patterns, and testing support to improve quality for all users.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="focus-areas">
  <h2>Focus areas</h2>
  <p>
    Our work includes WCAG alignment, inclusive content and interaction design, and capacity building through coaching and awareness.
  </p>
</section>

